UID:oP1Gx8nUGFbxMMPj8M6Yc
SUMMARY:Dirty Couch Brewing Anniversary Party
DTSTAMP:20260322T035029Z
DTSTART:20250510T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dirty Couch Brewing is celebrating our 10th anniversary and kic
	king off Seattle Beer Week! Come to celebrate with us at our Magnolia tapr
	oom on May 10. We will have new releases\, a pig roast\, and live music fr
	om our friends\, Grunge Tree.Festivities happening all day with food start
	ing around 3 pm and music at 6:30 pm.Dirty Couch Brewing is family and dog
	-friendly brewery specializing in unique barrel aged sours\, while craftin
	g more classic beer styles. We have a beer for every palate!\n\nFrom Seatt
	le Beer Week
